## Key Improvements Over Original

### **Visual Design**
| Aspect | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| **Component consistency** | Varied | Unified |
| **Icons** | Basic | Comprehensive |
| **Spacing** | Inconsistent | Standardized |
| **Colors** | Limited | Multiple variants |
| **Typography** | Mixed | Hierarchical |

### **Functionality**
| Feature | Before | After |
|---------|--------|-------|
| **Search** | None | Global search |
| **Presets** | None | Save/Load/Delete |
| **Validation** | Basic | Advanced |
| **Keyboard nav** | Partial | Full support |
| **Accessibility** | Basic | WCAG compliant |
| **Responsive** | Good | Optimized |

### **User Experience**
| Aspect | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| **Learning curve** | Steep | Gentle |
| **Discoverability** | Difficult | Easy (search) |
| **Efficiency** | Slow | Fast (presets) |
| **Error recovery** | Hard | Easy |
| **Mobile friendly** | OK | Excellent |

