## Implementation Guide

### **Step 1: Update a Single Page**

Example: ProfileSettingsPage

```tsx
import {
  SettingsPanel,
  FormGroup,
  AdvancedToggle,
  EnhancedInput,
  EnhancedSelect,
  SettingsPresets,
} from './index';

const ProfileSettingsPage: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <div className="space-y-6">
      <SettingsPanel
        title="Profile Information"
        description="Update your personal details"
      >
        <FormGroup label="Full Name" required>
          <EnhancedInput type="text" />
        </FormGroup>
      </SettingsPanel>
    </div>
  );
};
```

### **Step 2: Apply to All Pages**

The same pattern applies to all 11 existing pages:
1. General
2. Appearance
3. Profile
4. Security
5. Notifications
6. Accessibility
7. Usage Monitor
8. Users
9. Data
10. Globe
11. About

